featured_question.answer: From  Santipur station TOTO is available to go to Topkhana Masjid.It is situated at Sutragadr and near Sutragadr M.N.High School.Not so far from Santipur station,should reach within 10 minutes.

featured_reviews.review_id: Topkhana Masjid is an ancient Mosque of Santipur.Mogol Senani Gazi Yarr Mohammad had founded it in1695.It is situated near Sutragarh M.N.High School.It is in a distance nearabout 3km. from Shantipur station.Totos are available to visit this  historical place.At the time of Namaz you can see it with permission.There are beautiful Gambujes in this mosque.
